{
  "stem": "13313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't his-- it wasn't his instinctive point of view, because he was always a rebel and very, very proud and tough and very gutsy person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there weren't too many like him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't have too much company.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as long as we lived where we lived, and he made a decent living, and because he had established a marvelous relationship with most of our clientele, so they didn't abandon us, we-- we didn't know what was going to happen eventually.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody thought and hoped and felt that as long as we would cooperate, this was only a matter of time, and eventually, you know, like historically, this was only a period in our lives, and nothing really major would happen.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew better afterwards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, first of all, I was very young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was a very, I would say, quite authoritarian person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we weren't too much exposed to-- to news events.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they try not to have us hear what is going on, so we shouldn't be disturbed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened next was that we reached a point in time which I now realize was the-- was a result of the decision by the Nazi government to embark on the complete, on the so-called, quote, 'Final Solution.' So the effect of it was that there was a system to it.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German efficiency was also applied to-- the traditional German efficiency was applied to this exercise as well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first step was to have all-- all heads of families, able-bodied men, report for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were told that they should report, very short notice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything would be OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
